WEBVTT

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:24.500
"Love After Addiction"

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:26.600
(Episode 10)

00:01:34.239 --> 00:01:35.239
Thanks.

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:36.855
Brother Yoki, let's take a photo together.

00:01:36.879 --> 00:01:37.079
Sure.

00:01:37.159 --> 00:01:37.719
I'll take the photo for you guys.

00:01:37.799 --> 00:01:38.816
Over here, over here, over here!

00:01:38.840 --> 00:01:39.896
Look here, look here, come on.

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:40.680
Three, two, one!

00:01:40.840 --> 00:01:42.040
One more, one more, one more!

00:01:44.760 --> 00:01:45.280
Alright.

00:01:45.719 --> 00:01:46.640
Let's do it together, together!

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:47.239
The two of us, the two of us!

00:01:47.239 --> 00:01:48.079
Be good, be good.

00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:48.959
Let's take photos later, okay?

00:01:48.959 --> 00:01:49.680
We still have things to do.

00:01:49.719 --> 00:01:51.519
Be good, we'll take photos later.

00:01:51.959 --> 00:01:53.079
Alright, alright.

00:01:54.040 --> 00:01:55.040
Yoki.

00:01:55.239 --> 00:01:55.680
During this time,

00:01:55.681 --> 00:01:56.775
I've had a great time with you.

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:58.351
I hope it'll always be
smooth sailing for you,

00:01:58.375 --> 00:01:59.920
and you'll make
more and better works.

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:01.040
I'll always be your fan.

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:04.159
Happy wrap party!

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:05.656
I wish you a brilliant future
in the entertainment industry.

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:05.879
Ye Ran,

00:02:05.879 --> 00:02:06.439
This is my agent.

00:02:06.879 --> 00:02:07.879
Come, come, come.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:13.120
You guys...

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:16.280
Let's go,

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:19.639
dear brothers and sisters.

00:02:19.639 --> 00:02:20.639
It's been great.

00:02:22.479 --> 00:02:23.800
This past month

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:26.000
has been very hard

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:27.280
and now I announce:

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:28.919
Where are we going?

00:02:29.719 --> 00:02:30.719
Is a wrap!

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:33.400
Happy wrap party!

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:37.960
Our wrap today

00:02:38.039 --> 00:02:38.759
is not an end,

00:02:38.919 --> 00:02:39.919
I hope we can

00:02:40.039 --> 00:02:41.039
meet again someday.

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:43.039
Hope to see you all again in the future.

00:02:43.400 --> 00:02:45.159
See you!

00:02:46.159 --> 00:02:47.159
Let's go, let's go.

00:03:06.319 --> 00:03:06.759
Village Chief!

00:03:06.919 --> 00:03:08.039
Village Chief，Village Chief!

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:08.840
Little Meng.

00:03:09.360 --> 00:03:10.360
Brother Meng.

00:03:10.520 --> 00:03:11.520
Village Chief.

00:03:11.560 --> 00:03:12.560
Step aside, Xiao Mei.

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:13.800
Vil...

00:03:14.039 --> 00:03:15.039
Speak!

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:16.280
Say what?

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:18.000
Where's that bastard Yoki?

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:19.280
Village Chief

00:03:19.319 --> 00:03:20.759
Yoki wrapped his scenes today.

00:03:21.319 --> 00:03:22.359
What do you want with him?

00:03:23.159 --> 00:03:24.599
Now it's all over the internet

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:28.439
that the products we sold on
the live stream have quality issues.

00:03:28.879 --> 00:03:29.800
Some people are even smearing

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:30.960
our Lanwan Village seafood,

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:32.080
saying it's water-injected

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:33.680
and soaked in chemical solutions.

00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:34.919
It's toxic seafood!

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:36.199
Brother Meng!

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:38.256
Yoki was exposed for
faking the variety show

00:03:38.280 --> 00:03:40.159
which implicated our
village's products too.

00:03:40.537 --> 00:03:41.960
Just because of this,

00:03:42.439 --> 00:03:45.280
all of our huge village
seafood orders

00:03:45.560 --> 00:03:46.599
have all been cancelled.

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:47.639
Seafood

00:03:47.640 --> 00:03:49.000
isn't like other things,

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:50.440
we can't really take returns.

00:03:50.879 --> 00:03:51.879
This back and forth,

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:53.280
they'll all go bad on the way.

00:03:53.759 --> 00:03:55.439
Do you know what this means?

00:03:56.120 --> 00:03:56.479
Village Chief.

00:03:56.719 --> 00:03:57.199
Brother Meng

00:03:57.479 --> 00:03:58.599
I think the top priority now

00:03:58.800 --> 00:03:59.800
is to find Yoki

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:02.999
and find out the truth to
minimize our village's losses, right?

00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:05.280
Xiao Mei is right.

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:07.159
We're looking for Yoki

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:09.759
not to make him compensate
our losses or anything,

00:04:10.039 --> 00:04:12.000
but mainly to give everyone an explanation.

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:14.038
Yeah, that's right, that's right!

00:04:14.039 --> 00:04:15.919
If he was also cheated,

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:17.360
we have nothing to say.

00:04:17.879 --> 00:04:19.359
We'll never make things hard for him.

00:04:19.720 --> 00:04:20.720
We'll just accept it.

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:22.079
Let's go!

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:23.336
Village Chief, let's go, let's go!

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:24.680
Thank you for your understanding.

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:28.360
Brother Meng, what do we do?

00:04:39.536 --> 00:04:40.536
Mr. Yoki.

00:04:40.879 --> 00:04:42.040
How did I do this time?

00:04:43.319 --> 00:04:44.480
Are you satisfied?

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:50.920
Very well.

00:04:56.240 --> 00:04:57.240
Mr. Yoki

00:04:57.480 --> 00:04:59.000
I was wrong about what happened today.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:04:59.680
This variety show,

00:04:59.681 --> 00:05:00.896
I've been working
towards it for eight years.

00:05:00.920 --> 00:05:02.080
I don't want to lose my wife.

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:05.839
Will there be a second season of your show?

00:05:06.519 --> 00:05:07.519
What do you mean?

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:10.960
I'll continue to invest
in your second season.

00:05:14.639 --> 00:05:16.439
But regarding the
arrangement of this season.

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:21.319
I have a small suggestion.

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:26.040
Mr. Yoki.

00:05:27.279 --> 00:05:29.680
You're really hard on yourself.

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:34.519
Last time you stepped on a shell,

00:05:36.160 --> 00:05:37.680
I felt bad just watching.

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:40.120
And that time

00:05:41.319 --> 00:05:42.600
when you lived with Yang Meng,

00:05:44.759 --> 00:05:45.759
I drew the lots.

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:48.000
Pretty natural, right?

00:05:57.720 --> 00:05:59.560
And rescuing that little girl

00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:02.480
you and your team

00:06:04.600 --> 00:06:06.360
are truly amazing.

00:06:10.399 --> 00:06:11.399
These days.

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:13.600
You've worked hard.

00:06:14.639 --> 00:06:18.559
The next round of financing has
already been transferred to your account.

00:06:21.519 --> 00:06:22.680
Thank you, Mr. Yoki.

00:06:23.759 --> 00:06:24.759
Thank you so much.

00:06:25.959 --> 00:06:26.959
But.

00:06:27.519 --> 00:06:28.920
I just want to say one more thing.

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:31.279
You and Yang Meng,

00:06:32.399 --> 00:06:33.759
what exactly is your relationship?

00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:38.079
You've gone to so much trouble,

00:06:39.160 --> 00:06:40.600
Yang Meng is your...?

00:06:40.720 --> 00:06:41.720
High school classmate.

00:06:43.879 --> 00:06:45.720
High school classmate?

00:06:47.199 --> 00:06:48.680
Then Mr. Yoki,

00:06:50.079 --> 00:06:51.319
I wish you a good time!

00:06:51.952 --> 00:06:53.832
Have a good time!

00:06:54.439 --> 00:06:56.040
I'm very happy.

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:03.040
Mr. Yoki is having a great time.

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:06.519
You look really nice today.

00:07:10.399 --> 00:07:11.399
Yang Meng, I love you.

00:07:12.399 --> 00:07:13.399
Yang Meng, I love you.

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:16.879
High school classmate,
high school classmate!

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:17.959
Yang Meng, I love you.

00:07:17.959 --> 00:07:18.959
I love you.

00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:24.240
Village Chief.

00:07:24.519 --> 00:07:25.519
Village Chief.

00:07:25.720 --> 00:07:26.720
Have you found Yoki?

00:07:26.920 --> 00:07:27.920
Not yet.

00:07:30.852 --> 00:07:31.693
Little Meng,

00:07:31.839 --> 00:07:33.240
if we're being honest,

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:34.815
has helped the village so much.

00:07:34.839 --> 00:07:36.160
Repairing electrical appliances,

00:07:36.279 --> 00:07:37.679
and running errands over the years.

00:07:37.959 --> 00:07:39.039
During the seafood live streams

00:07:39.040 --> 00:07:40.815
it was all Little Meng who
helped arrange everything.

00:07:40.839 --> 00:07:41.759
You can't say that.

00:07:41.760 --> 00:07:42.935
If he hadn't let that wolf into the house，

00:07:42.959 --> 00:07:43.800
would our Lanwan Village's reputation

00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:44.199
get ruined?

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:44.920
When we were making money,

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:45.600
why didn't you say anything?

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:46.960
Did you take bribes from him?

00:07:47.079 --> 00:07:48.720
Which eye did you see me take it with?

00:07:49.199 --> 00:07:49.879
I've heard people say that.

00:07:49.959 --> 00:07:51.600
Little Meng helped us
repair the roof,

00:07:51.959 --> 00:07:54.199
why didn't you say anything then?

00:07:54.519 --> 00:07:55.815
Now that we're losing
money, you're blaming him.

00:07:55.839 --> 00:07:56.879
Alright, alright, alright!

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:57.600
Stop arguing!

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:59.320
If you keep arguing, my old bones

00:07:59.399 --> 00:08:00.399
will fall apart.

00:08:00.519 --> 00:08:01.079
Village Chief,

00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:02.640
Let me go look for him again.

00:08:03.319 --> 00:08:04.319
Go.

00:08:07.079 --> 00:08:08.799
Who would have thought that Lanwan Village,

00:08:09.279 --> 00:08:10.519
this century-old foundation,

00:08:11.199 --> 00:08:12.480
would be ruined by me.

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:14.800
Oh my god.

00:08:15.279 --> 00:08:16.279
Mr. Yoki.

00:08:16.519 --> 00:08:17.519
See you again someday.

00:08:26.759 --> 00:08:27.759
Are you crazy?

00:08:29.439 --> 00:08:30.639
Yoki Baby，Yoki Baby.

00:08:30.680 --> 00:08:31.439
Something happened!

00:08:31.639 --> 00:08:32.639
Look, look, look!

00:08:33.759 --> 00:08:35.159
That bitch Fang Xiaotian

00:08:35.399 --> 00:08:37.135
actually paid marketing
accounts to smear us!

00:08:37.159 --> 00:08:38.159
Distorting the truth!

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:41.096
Not only did she say that you going to
the fishing village to do public welfare

00:08:41.120 --> 00:08:42.120
was just for show,

00:08:42.200 --> 00:08:45.079
but she also said that
we orchestrated the whole rescue!

00:08:46.039 --> 00:08:46.519
It's okay.

00:08:46.679 --> 00:08:47.159
We'll handle this

00:08:47.159 --> 00:08:48.159
in a moment.

00:08:49.519 --> 00:08:50.960
Where are you going? My phone!

00:09:05.639 --> 00:09:06.639
Yang Meng.

00:09:21.879 --> 00:09:22.879
Grandma.

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:24.440
Has Yang Meng come home?

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:38.720
Where are you going?

00:09:39.639 --> 00:09:40.639
Can we leave now?

00:09:40.840 --> 00:09:41.320
Today,

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:42.320
we have to go back!

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:43.240
I can't leave.

00:09:43.639 --> 00:09:44.320
I need to find Yang Meng.

00:09:44.519 --> 00:09:45.240
Haven't you caused enough trouble

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:46.519
already?

00:09:46.960 --> 00:09:48.158
Don't you know these villagers

00:09:48.159 --> 00:09:49.240
are all watching you?

00:09:49.879 --> 00:09:50.959
Give me a little more time.

00:09:51.039 --> 00:09:52.039
You...

00:09:55.240 --> 00:09:56.240
Uncle Yang.

00:09:57.399 --> 00:09:58.399
Why are you here?

00:09:59.039 --> 00:09:59.879
If I hadn't come,

00:09:59.880 --> 00:10:01.216
something terrible might have happened.

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:02.240
Come with me.

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:07.000
I'm sorry.

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:09.440
I really have something
important to do right now.

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:18.960
Yang Meng.

00:10:21.799 --> 00:10:22.799
Yang Meng.

00:10:31.399 --> 00:10:32.399
Yang Meng

00:10:34.399 --> 00:10:35.399
Yang Meng.

00:11:38.600 --> 00:11:39.600
Yoki.

00:11:41.919 --> 00:11:42.919
Li Mei

00:11:42.960 --> 00:11:44.416
I'm sorry about what
happened in the village.

00:11:44.440 --> 00:11:45.159
But Yang Meng is missing.

00:11:45.240 --> 00:11:45.919
I need to find him right now.

00:11:46.039 --> 00:11:46.200
We...

00:11:46.201 --> 00:11:47.561
Stop talking about useless things.

00:11:48.320 --> 00:11:49.320
I came to find you.

00:11:50.879 --> 00:11:51.919
I know where Yang Meng is.

00:12:05.840 --> 00:12:07.200
Thank you for taking care of

00:12:07.440 --> 00:12:08.640
our Xiao Meng all these years.

00:12:08.960 --> 00:12:09.960
You've worked hard.

00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:19.080
It's him

00:12:20.440 --> 00:12:22.759
who has been taking care of us all along.

00:12:26.399 --> 00:12:27.440
Yang Meng.

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:33.480
Yang Meng.

00:12:36.879 --> 00:12:37.879
Yang Meng.

00:13:19.159 --> 00:13:20.159
Uncle, Uncle!

00:13:20.320 --> 00:13:21.320
Have you seen Yang Meng?

00:13:22.240 --> 00:13:23.799
He was standing on that reef earlier.

00:13:24.840 --> 00:13:25.279
Over there!

00:13:25.360 --> 00:13:25.679
There!

00:13:26.200 --> 00:13:27.200
Alright, alright.

00:13:28.480 --> 00:13:29.480
Oh, no.

00:13:30.679 --> 00:13:31.679
How do I get there?

00:13:31.799 --> 00:13:33.519
However you get there is how you get there.

00:13:39.480 --> 00:13:40.719
My boat, my boat!

00:13:40.720 --> 00:13:41.840
I'll give you a bigger boat!

00:13:42.120 --> 00:13:42.600
Wait for me to come back!

00:13:42.840 --> 00:13:43.279
Wait for me!

00:13:43.279 --> 00:13:44.279
Alright, it's yours.

00:14:02.879 --> 00:14:04.080
I'll be straight with you.

00:14:04.519 --> 00:14:05.039
Tell your son

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.759
to stop pestering Yoki.

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:07.879
Otherwise,

00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:09.639
don't blame me for being rude.

00:14:10.240 --> 00:14:11.240
What do you want?

00:14:11.799 --> 00:14:12.600
Simple.

00:14:12.759 --> 00:14:14.120
Keep your son in line.

00:14:14.919 --> 00:14:16.679
Shouldn't you keep your
own person in check?

00:14:44.720 --> 00:14:46.400
He rarely smiles like this in front of me.

00:14:49.759 --> 00:14:50.759
Look!

00:14:51.039 --> 00:14:52.759
How brightly he's smiling.

00:15:08.639 --> 00:15:11.519
In life,

00:15:13.200 --> 00:15:14.960
there are things we want to do，

00:15:16.080 --> 00:15:17.840
and things we don't.

00:15:18.799 --> 00:15:20.559
Things we can do，

00:15:21.519 --> 00:15:23.080
and things we cannot.

00:15:24.679 --> 00:15:26.399
Some things we want to do，

00:15:27.320 --> 00:15:28.320
we simply can't，

00:15:28.852 --> 00:15:29.931
and aren't allowed to.

00:15:31.879 --> 00:15:33.440
And some things we don't want to do，

00:15:34.200 --> 00:15:35.200
since they fall to us，

00:15:35.679 --> 00:15:37.039
we have to do them anyway.

00:15:37.064 --> 00:15:40.544
[TN: I'm guessing these reminders
are all notes Yang Meng left Grandma]

00:15:49.200 --> 00:15:50.200
Yang Meng.

00:15:56.559 --> 00:15:57.559
Yang Meng.

00:16:01.320 --> 00:16:02.320
Yang Meng.

00:16:07.360 --> 00:16:08.360
Yang Meng.

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:24.000
What are you doing here?

00:16:26.039 --> 00:16:27.239
Don't you know it's dangerous?

00:16:28.399 --> 00:16:30.079
I've been looking for you for a long time.

00:16:36.559 --> 00:16:37.559
I'm going back.

00:16:42.080 --> 00:16:43.320
I want you to come with me.

00:16:44.759 --> 00:16:45.759
I will go back.

00:16:48.399 --> 00:16:49.399
Then come down!

00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:51.240
No.

00:16:51.279 --> 00:16:52.279
Don't move!

00:16:52.639 --> 00:16:53.839
I'll come over to pick you up.

00:16:53.879 --> 00:16:54.879
Don't move!

00:16:55.759 --> 00:16:56.759
Don't move!

00:16:59.200 --> 00:17:00.200
But not with you.

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:05.760
What's wrong with you again?

00:17:07.480 --> 00:17:08.800
Isn't everything fine between us?

00:17:10.119 --> 00:17:11.119
Yoki.

00:17:13.680 --> 00:17:15.279
What's your real purpose
in being here?

00:17:19.160 --> 00:17:20.240
I'm here for you!

00:17:26.119 --> 00:17:27.119
For me?

00:17:31.359 --> 00:17:32.480
Hiding shoes on the beach,

00:17:33.480 --> 00:17:34.520
getting pricked by shells,

00:17:35.640 --> 00:17:36.656
changing the living place,

00:17:36.680 --> 00:17:37.879
including hiding that little girl...

00:17:37.880 --> 00:17:39.160
It was all your plan, wasn't it?

00:17:40.200 --> 00:17:41.200
Wasn't it?

00:17:43.160 --> 00:17:44.160
Wasn't it?

00:17:45.680 --> 00:17:46.680
Yang Meng

00:17:46.759 --> 00:17:47.160
Yang Meng

00:17:47.759 --> 00:17:48.759
Yoki.

00:17:49.640 --> 00:17:51.680
Do you take me for a fool?

00:17:56.319 --> 00:17:56.920
When everyone else

00:17:57.039 --> 00:17:57.880
was doubting you,

00:17:57.960 --> 00:17:58.960
only I thought

00:17:59.000 --> 00:18:00.319
you weren't that kind of person.

00:18:03.559 --> 00:18:04.559
Only me!

00:18:05.200 --> 00:18:07.480
To whitewash your image,
you really went to great lengths.

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:09.960
Yang Meng.

00:18:10.079 --> 00:18:11.359
You're so selfish! Listen to me.

00:18:16.039 --> 00:18:17.039
But it's okay.

00:18:19.640 --> 00:18:20.640
It's not your fault.

00:18:22.039 --> 00:18:23.039
It's my fault.

00:18:25.839 --> 00:18:28.119
It's my fault for liking you so much.

